<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9ac5b53-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s36c"><num value="36c">§ 36c.</num><heading> Acceptance of contributions from public and private sources; cooperation with other agencies in prosecution of projects</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In fiscal year 1987 and thereafter the United States Geological Survey is authorized to accept lands, buildings, equipment, and other contributions from public and private sources and to prosecute projects in cooperation with other agencies, Federal, State, or private.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc9ac5b54-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/500/s101/h/tI">Pub. L. 99–500, § 101(h) [title I]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-18">Oct. 18, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1783-242">100 Stat. 1783–242</ref>, 1783–252, and <ref href="/us/pl/99/591/s101/h/tI">Pub. L. 99–591, § 101(h) [title I]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-30">Oct. 30, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3341-242">100 Stat. 3341–242</ref>, 3341–252; <ref href="/us/pl/102/154/tI">Pub. L. 102–154, title I</ref>, <date date="1991-11-13">Nov. 13, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/1000">105 Stat. 1000</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
